        "name": "Fey Glamour",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "You call upon fey glamours to cloak an area or the targets in illusion. This has the effect of either *illusory scene* on the area or *illusory disguise* on the creatures, as if heightened to a rank 1 rank lower than *fey glamour*, and using *fey glamour's* range and duration.",
